<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Portfolio Page</title>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Ron's Portfolio</h1>
        <p>Frontend Developer and Designer</p>
        <hr>
    </header>

    <main>
        <section id="about">
           <h2>About Me</h2>
           <p> Hello I am Ron, a passionate web Developer
            with expertise in building interative and structured web pages
           </p>
        </section>

        <section id="projects">
            <h2>My Projects</h2>
            <article>
                <h3>Project 1: Personal Blog</h3>
                <p>A semantic blog website built using only HTML</p>
            </article>

            <article>
                <h3>Project 2: Online Store</h3>
                <p>A product listing page with multiple categories
                    and products
                </p>
            </article>

            <article>
                <h3>Project 3: Portfolio Layout</h3>
                <p>This portfolio is an example of structured 
                    HTML layout
                </p>
            </article>

        </section>

        <section>

        <h2>Contact Me</h2>
        <form action="#">

        <label for="name">Name:</label>
        <br>
        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
        <br><br>

        <label for="email">Email:</label>
        <br>
        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
        <br><br>

        <label for="message">Message</label><br>
        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" cols="30"
        required></textarea><br><br>

        <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
        </form>
        </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
        <hr>
        <p>copy; 2026 Ron's Portfolio  Contact:ron@example.com</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
